afternoon in southwest moscows vostryakovskoye cemetery 
several hundred people gathered outside sakharovs apartment 
building friday evening holding candles and wreathing his 
photograph in flowers memorial services were scheduled sunday at 
the citys main youth center and on monday at the lebedev physics 
institute where sakharov worked and the academy of sciences of 
