declined to endorse the service until further review 
acces has the potential to be an outstanding product added 
dunaway principal of benjamin russell high school in alexander 
city ala he said his school has not subscribed because of 
concerns over the security of the information given by the students 
and the time needed for the students to complete the survey 
as for security frazier said only postsecondary institutions 
accredited by bodies recognized by the department of education or 
the council on postsecondary accreditation are eligible to 
subscribe to the network state employment and training agencies 
also can join so students can learn about job training 
opportunities or internships he said 
