referring to the issue of german reunification the joint 
declaration stated that our basic principle is the peoples right 
to selfdetermination to which the east germans are also entitled 
however it added that german reunification can only be 
realized as part of the european process of integration 
the groups further declared a common goal of eliminating all 
vestiges of stalinism 
they said they want to set up an international forum to 
coordinate their activities and called on all democratic 
