all seven of the suspects rodriguez gachas body was found 
gripping a submachine gun emptied in the battle the report said 
it did little to clear up conflicting versions of how police 
discovered rodriguez gachas whereabouts 
bogotas la prensa newspaper quoting a reporter who accompanied 
